issue.body:
I receive the following error message:

Failed to create directory "C:\xampp\htdocs\yii\frontend\web\assets\ **1bc5b209\assets\1bc5b209\assets\1bc5b209\assets\1bc5b209\assets\1bc5b209\assets\1bc5b209\assets\1bc5b209\assets\1bc5b209\assets\1bc5b209\assets\1bc5b209\assets\1bc5b209\assets\1bc5b209\assets\1bc5b209\assets\1bc5b209** ": mkdir(): No such file or directory

after defining the sourcePath in \yii\frontend\assets\AppAsset.php:

```
namespace ap1_epas\assets;

use yii\web\AssetBundle;

class AppAsset extends AssetBundle {

    public $sourcePath = '@webroot';
    // public $basePath = '@webroot';
    // public $baseUrl = '@web';
    public $css = [
        'css/fix_bootstrap.css',
        'css/light.css',
        'css/toastr.min.css',
        'css/font-awesome.css',
    ];
    public $js = [
        'js/jquery.blockUI.js',
        'js/jquery.cookie.js',
        'js/toastr.min.js',
        'js/custom.js',
    ];
    public $jsOptions = array(
        'position' => \yii\web\View::POS_HEAD
    );
    public $depends = [
        'yii\web\YiiAsset',
        'yii\bootstrap\BootstrapAsset',
    ];
}
```

In the directory \yii\frontend\web\assets is created a new directory **1bc5b209**, which contains directory **assets**, which contains directory **1bc5b209**, ...

